# Vehicle GPS Tracking API

A RESTful API for GPS tracking and monitoring of vehicles, built using Java Spring Boot, secured with JWT authentication, and documented using Swagger.

---

## ğŸ›  Tech Stack

- Java Spring Boot
- Javax Validator
- JWT (JSON Web Token)
- PostgreSQL
- Docker & Docker Compose
- Swagger (API Documentation)
- Git

